data.description: New Charming 3-Bedroom, 2-Bath Home waiting for it's  new owners!    This home is nestled within the secure and welcoming confines of the gated Dogwood South community. This home enjoys the serenity of a cul-de-sac location while being just moments away from the conveniences of Haughton, and a short drive from Shreveport-Bossier City.  Step through the front door and into a spacious, open concept living area with high ceilings and large windows that flood the space with natural light. The living room features a cozy fireplace, creating the perfect atmosphere for gatherings and relaxation. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample counter space, and a breakfast bar, ideal for preparing and sharing meals with family and friends. As a resident of Dogwood South, you'll have access to community amenities including a swimming pool, clubhouse, and a friendly atmosphere.  This area qualifies for Rural Development which means possible 0 dollars down payment!  Call today for details!
